data.description: Welcome to this charming brick ranch nestled in the heart of Stone Mountain, Georgia. This delightful property boasts a spacious and inviting atmosphere, sitting proudly on a large lot that provides ample space for all your outdoor desires. With 3 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, there's plenty of room for your family and guests. As you approach the property, you'll be captivated by the classic brick faoade that exudes timeless appeal. Upon entry, you'll find a world of possibilities to make this home truly your own. The layout allows for seamless flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas. Imagine designing your dream kitchen with modern appliances and fixtures, creating a space that's perfect for culinary adventures and gatherings with loved ones. The three spacious bedrooms offer comfort and privacy. The master suite comes complete with its own private bathroom, providing a serene retreat at the end of the day. The two additional bedrooms are ideal for family members or guests, with easy access to the remaining bathrooms. One of the standout features of this property is the large lot. Whether you envision a lush garden oasis, a play area for kids and pets, or even a tranquil outdoor entertainment space, the possibilities are endless. There's plenty of room for a pool, a garden shed, or whatever your heart desires. This home is ready for updates, allowing you to put your personal touch on every aspect of the property. With a little creativity and some renovation work, you can transform this charming ranch into the home of your dreams.
